description:
Here comes part 3 of our Skaven mega review, covering the new Skaven Brood Terror model, the repulsive Clan Moulder Master Moulder, and the spectacular Vizzik Skour, Prophet of the Horned Rat. We share high-res sprue images and take a look at all the assembly options and optional bitz.

The post Review: Skaven Brood Terror, Master Moulder & Vizzik Skour, Prophet of the Horned Rat appeared first on Tale of Painters.
title: Review: Skaven Brood Terror, Master Moulder & Vizzik Skour, Prophet of the Horned Rat
